### CCR-029 — CC Launch Flow
###
### 검증:
### - POST /tables/{id}/launch 응답에 launch_token, cc_instance_id, ws_url
### - launch_token JWT 만료 5분
### - WebSocket 연결 시 launch_token 검증 + cc_instance_id 매칭
### - Operator assigned_tables RBAC
### - TableFSM SETUP 이상 요구

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@operator_token = {{$dotenv OPERATOR_JWT}}
@viewer_token = {{$dotenv VIEWER_JWT}}

### 30.1 POST /api/v1/tables/1/launch-cc — Admin 정상
# @name launchAdmin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1/launch-cc
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": {
#     "table_id": 1,
#     "status": "live",
#     "cc_instance_id": "cc-uuid-abcd-1234",
#     "launch_token": "eyJhbGc...",         // JWT 5분 수명
#     "ws_url": "ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc?table_id=1",
#     "launched_at": "2026-04-10T12:00:00Z"
#   },
#   "error": null
# }

### 30.2 launch_token JWT decode 검증 (수동)
###
### 응답의 launch_token 을 jwt.io 등에서 디코드:
###   sub = cc_instance_id
###   exp = 현재 + 5분 (300s)
###   role = "cc_launch"
###   table_id = 1
###
### 5분 후 재연결 시도 → 401 (expired)

### 30.3 POST /api/v1/tables/1/launch-cc — Viewer → 403
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1/launch-cc
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상: 403 Forbidden (Viewer는 Launch 불가)

### 30.4 POST — Operator + 할당되지 않은 테이블 → 403
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/999/launch-cc
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# Operator의 assigned_tables 에 999가 없을 때:
# 예상: 403 Forbidden (RBAC 거부)

### 30.5 POST — TableFSM == EMPTY → 422
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/99/launch-cc
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# Table 99 가 EMPTY 상태 (게임 설정 전):
# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity
# { "error": "INVALID_TABLE_STATE", "current_state": "EMPTY", "required": "SETUP|LIVE|PAUSED" }

### 30.6 WebSocket 연결 with launch_token (수동)
###
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc?table_id=1&token={{launchAdmin.response.body.data.launch_token}}&cc_instance_id={{launchAdmin.response.body.data.cc_instance_id}}&format=json'
###
### 예상: 연결 성공 후 초기 상태 JSON 수신:
### {
###   "type": "InitialState",
###   "payload": {
###     "table": {...},
###     "seats": [...],
###     "current_hand": {...} | null
###   }
### }

### 30.7 WebSocket 연결 — cc_instance_id 불일치
###
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc?table_id=1&token=<launch_token>&cc_instance_id=wrong-uuid&format=json'
###
### 예상: 연결 즉시 종료 (1008 Policy Violation)
### 이유: launch_token 의 sub 와 cc_instance_id 가 불일치

### 30.8 WebSocket 연결 — 만료된 launch_token
###
### (launch 후 5분+ 경과)
### wscat -c 'ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc?table_id=1&token=<expired>&cc_instance_id=...&format=json'
###
### 예상: 1008 Policy Violation (TOKEN_EXPIRED)
### 클라이언트는 Lobby에 재요청 필요
